longBusinessSummary: Gnomestar Craft Inc. engages in the production and distribution of cannabis product for medical and recreational use in Canada. The company was formerly known as Vodis Pharmaceuticals Inc. and changed its name to Gnomestar Craft Inc. in December 2020. Gnomestar Craft Inc. was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Delta, Canada.
